                        <interp inst="t18490507-name-151" type="given" value="HENRY"></interp>HENRY SLIM</persName>
                  </hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">re-examined</hi>, I did not know the prisoner when he had his money, but I have heard that he had a considerable sum of money, which he squandered away—he was certainly once in a condition to have lent 12<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. or 20<hi rend="italic">l</hi>.—I employed him, as he was without friends or victuals—I do not wish to press the charge against him.</p>
